title: UPDATE: SUSPECTED KILLER FOUND! Newborn baby girl, umbilical cord still attached, dies alone in metal trash drum sucking her thumb for comfort. WHO LEFT HER TO DIE?
itunes:title: UPDATE: SUSPECTED KILLER FOUND! Newborn baby girl, umbilical cord still attached, dies alone in metal trash drum sucking her thumb for comfort. WHO LEFT HER TO DIE?
description:
Body of an infant baby girl found in a metal trash can. Who left her there? Nancy Grace talks with a panel of experts on an arrest in the case of Baby Jane Doe. Our panel includes: Ashley Wilcott, Judge and trial attorney; Joseph Scott Morgan, Forensic Expert: Dr. Michelle Dupre, Medical Examiner; Shera LaPoint, Genetic Genealogist; Major Wendell Raborn,  Iberia Parish Sheriff's office; Catalean Theriot, Comprehensive Victim Intervention Specialist Louisiana 16th Judicial District Attorney's Office; and  KADN News 15 Reporter Leigha McNeil
